act={'137':['Fraudulently travelling or attempting to travel without proper pass or ticket.', '(1) Shall be punishable with imprisonment for a term which may extend to SIX MONTHS, or with fine which may extend to Rs. 1,000/-, or with both.', '(3) Shall be liable to pay the excess charge referred to in sub-section (2) shall be a sum equal to the ordinary single fae referred to in that sub-section or Rs. 250/- whichever is more.', '(4) Shall suffer imprisonment for a term which may extend to SIX MONTH.'],
     '138':['Levy of excess charge and fare for travelling without proper pass or ticket or beyond authorised distance.', '(1) Shall be liable to pay, the excess charge mentioned in sub-section (3) in addition to the odinary single fare for the distance which he has travelled.', '(2) Shall be liable to pay, any difference between the fare paid by him and the fare payable in respect of the journery he has made and the excess charge referred to in sub-section (3).'],
     '141':['Needlessly interfeing with means of communication in a train.', 'Shall be punishable with imprisonment for a term whih may extend to ONE YEAR, or with fine which may extend to Rs. 1,000/-, or with both. Where a passenger, without reasonable and sufficient cause, makes use of the alarm chain povided by a railway administration, such punishment shall not be less than a fine of Rs. 500/- in the case of conviction for the first offence and imprisionment for THREE MONTHS, in case of conviction for the second or subsequent offence.'], 
     '142':['Penalty for transfer of tickets', '(1) Shall be punishable with imprisonment for a term which may extend to THREE MONTHS, or with fine which may extend to Rs. 500/- or with both and shall also forfeit the ticket which he sells or attempts to sell or parts or attempts to part.', '(2) Shall be punishable with imprisonment for a term which may extend to THREE MONTHS and with fine which may extend to Rs. 500/- and if the purchaser or holder of any ticket aforesaid travels or attempts to travel therewith, he shall forfeit the ticket which he so purchased or obtained and shall be deemed to be travelling without a proper ticket and shall be liable to be dealt with unde section 138. Provided that in the absence of special and adequate reasons to the contrary to be mentioned in the punishment under sub-sequestion (1) or sub-section (2) shall not be less than a fine of Rs. 250/-.'],
     '143':['Penalty for unauthorised carrying on of bun isess of procuring and supplying of railway tickets.', 'He shall be punishabale with imprisionment for a term which may extend to THREE YEARS or with fine which may extend to Rs. 10,000/-, or with bhoth, and shall also forfeit the tickets which he so procures, supplies, purhsers, sells or attempts to purchase or sell.', 'Provided that in the absence of special and adequate reasons to the contrary to be mentioned in the judgment of the Court, such punishment shall not be less than imprisonment for a term of one month or  a fine of Rs. 5000/-.' '(2) Whoever abets any offence punishable under this section shall be punishable withthe same punishment as is provided for the offence.'],
     '144':['Prohibition on hawking, etc., and begging.', 'Shall be punishable with imprisonment for a term which may wextend to ONE YEAR, or with fine which may extgend to Rs. 2000/-, or with both.', 'Provided that, in the absence of special and adequate reasons to the contrary to be mentioned in the judgment of the Court, such punishment shall not be less than a fine of Rs. 1,000/-.', '(2) Shall be punishment as provided under sub-section (1).'],
     '145':['Drunkenness or nuisance.', 'He may be removed from the railway by wany railway servant and shall, in addition to the forfeiture of his pass or ticket, be punishable with imprisonment which may extend to SIX MONTHS, and with fine which may extend to rS. 500/-', 'Provided that in the absence of special and adequate reasons to the contrary to be mentioned in the judgment of the Court, such punishment shall not be less than (a) af fine of Rs. 100/- in the case of conviction for the first offence; and (b) imprisonment of ONE MONTH and a fine of Rs. 250/- , in the case of conviction for second or subsequent offence.'],
     '146':['Obstructing railway servant in his duties.', 'Shall be punishable with imprisonment for a term which may extend to SIX MONTHS, or with fine which may kextend to Rs. 1,000/- or with both.'],
     '147':['Trespass and fefusal to desist from trespass.', '(1) Shall be punishable with imprisonment for a term which may extend to SIX MONTHS, or with fine which may extend to rS. 1,000/-, or with both.', 'Provided that in the absence of special and adequate reasons to the contrary to be mentioned in the judgment of the Court, such punishment shall not be less than a fine of Rs. 500/-.'],
     '148':['Penanty for making a false claim for compensation.', 'Shall be punishable with imprisonment for a tem which may extend to THREE YEARS, or with fine, or with both.'],
     '149':['Making a false claim for compensation.', 'Shall be punishable with imprisonment for a tem which may extend to THREE YEARS, or with fine, or with both.'],
     '150':['Malicious wrecking or attempting to wreck a train.', 'Shall be pubishable with imprisonment for life, or with figorous imprisonment for a term whih may extend to TEN YEARS.', 'Provided that in the absence of special and adequate reasons to the contrary to be mentioned in the judgment of the Court, where a person is punishable with rigorous imprisonment, such imprisonment shall not be less than (a) THREE YEARS, in the case of a conviction for the first offence. (b) SEVEN YEARS, in the case of conviction for the sectiond or subsequent offence.'],
     '151':['Damage to or destruction of certain railway properties.', '(1) Shall be punishable with imprisonment for a term which may esxtend to FIVE YEARS, or with fine, or with both.'],
     '152':['Maliciously hurting or attempting to hurt persons travelling by railway.', 'Shall be punishable with imprisonment for life, or with imprisonment for a term which may esxtend to TEN YEARS.'],
     '153':['Endangering safety of persons tragvelling by railway by wilful act or omission.', 'Shall be punishable with imprisonment for a term which may extend to FIVE YEARS.'],
     '154':['Endangering safety of persons travelling by railway by rash or negligent act or imilssion.', 'Shall be punishable with imprisonment for a term which may extend to ONE YEAR, or with fine or with both.'],
     '155':['Entering into a compartment resrved or resisting entry into a compartment not reserved.', '(1) Shall be punishable with imprisonment for a term which may extend to FIVE YEARS.', '(2) Shall be punishable with fine which may extend to Rs. 200/-.'],
     '156':['Travelling on roof, step or engine of a train.', 'Shall be punishable with imprisonment for a term which may exstend to THREE MONTHS, or with fine which may extend to Rs. 500/-, or with both and may be removed from the railway by any railway servant.'],
     '157':['Altering or defacing pass or ticket.', 'Shall be punishable with imprisonment for a term which may extend to THREE MONTHS, or with fine which may extend to Rs. 500/-, or with both.'],
     '158':['Penalty for contravention of any of the provisions of Chapter XIV', 'Shall be punishable with fine which may exrtend to Rs. 500/-.'],
     '159':['Disobedience of drivers or condoctor of vehiles to directions of raileway servant, etc.', 'Shall be punishable with imprisonment for a term which may extend to ONE MONTH, or with fine which may extend to Rs. 500/- or with both.'],
     '160':['Opening or breaking a level crossing gate.', '(1) Shall be punishable with imprisonment for a term which may extend to THREE YEARS.', '(2) Shall be punishable with imprisonment for a term whih may extend to FIVE YEARS.'],


    }